{
  "texts": [
    "In addition to the numerous educational opportunities associated with ChatGPT, there has also been research conducted on its drawbacks and challenges.",
    "Hosseini et al. (2024) queried ChatGPT and suggested that any section written by a natural language processing system like ChatGPT should be checked by a domain expert for accuracy, bias, relevance, and reasoning and if it contains errors or biases.",
    "Furthermore, coauthors need to be held accountable for its accuracy, cogency, and integrity.",
    "Mhlanga (2023a) analysed the responsible and ethical usage of ChatGPT in his literature review.",
    "To start with, educators must inform students about data collection, security measures and the limitations of AI to foster critical thinking."
  ]
}